    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and chop the <strong>potatoes </strong>into large, bite-sized pieces and add to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiling water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, cook for 10-15 min or until the potatoes are fork-tender then drain, return to the pot and set aside</p>",
