    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim, then slice the <strong>spring onions</strong> finely</p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks, keeping the <strong>leaves</strong> and <strong>stalks </strong>separate</p>",
